<Objects>
  <!-- Ordinary Client - ASGARD dungeon bosses (Phase C content).
       RECONSTRUCTED from recovered video (verbatim taunts live in BehaviorDb.Asgard.cs).
       The 2019 client rip lacks these post-2019 entities, so: stats are DESIGNED, and
       SPRITES are PLACEHOLDERS (reskinned from chars16x16dEncounters2) to be replaced with
       real Asgard art later. Projectiles reuse existing descriptors (Thunder Swirl/Trident)
       so they render on both server and client. Type ids 0x8fe0-0x8fe5 (free). -->
